      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit boasts a linear power band and exceptional throttle response thanks to its individual throttle body arrangement. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including rod bearing replacement and a recent fluid service for the M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-specified rigidity with no subframe issues, and the suspension geometry remains true for precise cornering. A driver-focused example that prioritizes mechanical integrity and visceral performance over garage-queen aesthetics.",
